'''Chad''' ke [[naga]] [[lefasana|lefasaneng]] la [[Afrika]]. Cameroon e bogare bodikela bja Afrika, e wela seleteng sa [[Bogare bja Afrika]].

Chad e agišane le :
* [[Libya]] (leboa),
* [[Sudan]] (bohlabela),
* [[Central African Republic]] (borwa),
* [[Cameroon]] (borwa bodikela),
* [[Nigeria]] (borwa bodikela),
* [[Niger]] (bodikela).

